title: Agility/Level up table
content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Agility/Level up table

  • The player's Agility level determines how quickly run energy regenerates over time. The regeneration rate increases every 6 levels. It is further boosted by wearing pieces of the graceful set, up to 30% with the full outfit. For more information, see the Energy article.
